Class AuthIconBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • ru.baronessdev.paid.auth.api.gui.AuthIconBuilder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BaronessAuthAPIComponent

    public class AuthIconBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
implements BaronessAuthAPIComponent
    Builder для создания иконок GUI.

    Пример использования: 

     
 new AuthIconBuilder(new YourIconExecutor)
     .setType(Material.APPLE)
     .setTitle("click me")
     .setLore("please", "just click")
     .build();
    See Also:
    AuthIconsAPI, AuthIconExecutor
